             was indicted for <rs id="t17990109-52-off294" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990109-52-off294" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990109-52-off294" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990109-52-cd295" type="crimeDate">17th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990109-52-off294 t17990109-52-cd295"></join>, a stock-bed, value 4s. and a woollen blanket, value 1s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17990109-52-victim423" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Evans
               <interp inst="t17990109-52-victim423" type="surname" value="Evans"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990109-52-victim423" type="given" value="John"></interp>
