                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990109-52-defend422 t17990109-52-punish300"></join>
               fined 1s. and discharged
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
